p: The TCID50 of brain leachate was only detected at 6 dpi in the A/Guangdong/GZ8H002/2017(H7N9)-infected mice ( Figure 5D). In the A/Guangdong/GZ8H002/2017(H7N9)-infected mice, live virus was isolated from the brain leachate at 6 dpi. However, the H7N9 virus could not be isolated from the brain leachate of the A/Zhejiang/DTID-ZJU01/2013(H7N9)-infected mice ( Table 2).
